Description
org.phenopackets.phenopackettools.builder
A module with pre-defined ontology constants, convenience methods, and concise builders to simplify phenopacket construction.

A module for converting between the PhenopacketSchemaVersions.
org.phenopackets.phenopackettools.core
The module defines core concepts shared by (almost) all modules of phenopacket-tools.
org.phenopackets.phenopackettools.io
A module for reading and writing top-level elements of Phenopacket Schema.

A module with example phenopackets suitable for unit tests.

A module with utility functions.

Defines the base APIs for phenopacket validation.

Defines a ValidationWorkflowRunner with base validation backed by a JSON schema.
